{"article_id":"Ph9U02u3fcL1K12y","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Missouri state trooper in charge","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"of directing the law enforcement response to protests","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that have rocked a St. Louis suburb","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"slammed `` violent agitators ''","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"who","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"were using largely peaceful protests as `` cover ''","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to commit criminal acts .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Missouri Highway Patrol Capt . Ron Johnson told reporters in Ferguson early Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that 31 people had been arrested during a night of unrest","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that followed a day of largely peaceful protest .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"As Johnson spoke ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"two handguns and a Molotov cocktail","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"had been confiscated during the night by authorities","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"lay on a table in front of him .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The majority-black town of approximately 21,000 has been roiled by unrest since the death of 18-year-old Michael Brown ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"who was fatally shot by a white police officer","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"following a confrontation of some kind on the afternoon of August 9 .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Local authorities have fired tear gas and smoke canisters on an almost daily basis at protesters","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"upset with the response to the shootings by Ferguson Police .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"A visibly angry Johnson said","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"that officers had come under heavy gunfire from protesters","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"and at least two people had been shot .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"Johnson said","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"he did not know the condition of the shooting victims .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Four officers had been injured","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"when they were struck by rocks or bottles ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"though Johnson claimed","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"that police had not fired a single shot .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Citing what he called a `` dangerous dynamic in the night , ''","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"Johnson requested","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"that protests take place during the daylight hours ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"so that officers could effectively isolate any troublemakers .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"However , Johnson said","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"that his forces could not make protesters leave the streets after sunset","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"if they did not want to .","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"`` This nation is watching each and every one of us , ''","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"said Johnson .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"`` I am not going to let the criminals","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"that have come here from across this country ,","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"or live in this neighborhood ,","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"define this community . ''","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"Johnson added","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"that some of those","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"who had been arrested overnight","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"had come from as far afield as New York and California .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"The trooper also directed his wrath at the assembled media ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that they had put themselves and officers in danger","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"by failing to clear areas","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"when asked","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"before imploring them to `` not glamorize the acts of criminals . ''","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"`` We do not want to lose another life in this community , ''","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Johnson added .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Shortly before midnight local time , the St. Louis Post-Dispatch reported","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that police fired tear gas at a group of protesters","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"who had reportedly defied orders","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"to leave the parking lot of a burned-out QuikTrip convenience store","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"that has been near the center of demonstrations over the past eight day .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"St. Louis County Police Chief Sam Dotson told reporters","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that shots had been fired in the area","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and media members were told to go to a designated area about a quarter of a mile away .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Late Monday , reporters estimated","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that the number of protesters had dropped to around 100 , far fewer than the number of media members","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"who were covering them .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"A photographer for the Getty photo agency was arrested","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"while covering the demonstrations","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"and later released .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Two German reporters were arrested","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"and detained for three hours .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"Conservative German daily Die Welt said","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"correspondent Ansgar Graw and reporter Frank Herrmann ,","depth":17},{"id":74,"text":"who writes for German regional papers ,","depth":17},{"id":75,"text":"were arrested","depth":16},{"id":76,"text":"after allegedly failing to follow police instructions","depth":16},{"id":77,"text":"to vacate an empty street .","depth":16},{"id":78,"text":"They said","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"they followed police orders .","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"At his news conference , Johnson said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"in some cases it was not immediately clear who was a reporter","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"but that","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"once it was established ,","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"police acted properly .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"As darkness fell ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"National Guard units with armored vehicles were waiting at a staging area about a half-mile from the portion of West Florissant Avenue","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that has been the scene of the largest protests .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Closer to the protest site , a crowd of demonstrators was marching","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"and growing in size .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Sheriff 's deputies in body armor and state troopers","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"carrying wooden bats and gas masks","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"stood watch over the group .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"The Post-Dispatch reported","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that some protesters began throwing bottles at police shortly after 10 p.m. local time .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Authorities responded","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"by ordering protesters to clear the streets","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"and firing high-pitched sound cannons .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Another group of protesters marched toward the police lines","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"and stopped ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"defying orders","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that demonstrators could not assemble in a single spot ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"but had to keep moving instead .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"The Post-Dispatch reported","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"that an armored vehicle moved down the street","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"trying to clear the crowd","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"and a group of pastors locked arms","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and helped to move protesters away from the police line .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"In federal court earlier Monday , a judge denied a request from the American Civil Liberties Union for a restraining order","depth":4},{"id":109,"text":"that would have prevented authorities from enforcing the no-stopping rule .","depth":4},{"id":110,"text":"A grand jury could begin hearing evidence Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"to determine","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"whether the officer , Darren Wilson , should be charged in Brown 's death ,","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"said Ed Magee , spokesman for St. Louis County 's prosecuting attorney .","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"The St. Louis County medical examiner 's autopsy found","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"that Brown was shot six to eight times in the head and chest ,","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"office administrator Suzanne McCune said Monday .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"But she declined further comment ,","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"the full findings were not expected for about two weeks .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Lawyers for Brown 's family and hired pathologists said","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"an independent autopsy determined","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"that Brown was shot six times ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"including twice in the head .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"Forensic pathologist Shawn Parcells ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"who assisted former New York City chief medical examiner Dr. Michael Baden during the private autopsy ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"a bullet grazed Brown 's right arm .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"the wound indicates","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"Brown may have had his back to the shooter ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"or he could have been facing the shooter","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"with his hands above his head or in a defensive position across his chest or face .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"`` We do n't know , ''","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Parcells said .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"`` We still have to look at the other","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"( elements )","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"of this investigation","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"before we start piecing things together . ''","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"A third and final autopsy was performed Monday for the Justice Department by one of the military 's most experienced medical examiners ,","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Attorney General Eric Holder","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"said .","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"Holder was scheduled to travel to Ferguson later this week","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"to meet with FBI and other officials","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"carrying out an independent federal investigation into Brown 's death .","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"Due to the unrest , the Ferguson-Florissant School District announced late Monday","depth":3},{"id":146,"text":"that classes would be canceled for the remainder of the week .","depth":3},{"id":147,"text":"Students were due to return from summer vacation last week ,","depth":3},{"id":148,"text":"but were held out due to the unrest .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":297,"left":293,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":258,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":256,"right":257,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":165,"right":255,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":156,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":152,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":151,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":158,"right":163,"relat